cantrip-bandage-name = Haemostatic Assistance
cantrip-bandage-description = Procures means to assist with stemming a bleeding wound.

cantrip-antidote-name = Botanical Rejuvenating
cantrip-antidote-description = Procures a substance to mend vitality of a plant.

cantrip-chese-name = Cheese
cantrip-cheese-description = Summon cheese from a dimension with infinite cheese.

cantrip-mop-name = Cleansing Aura
cantrip-mop-description = Removes filth around you. Like a tiny cleanade. Only affects tiles adjacent to where you stand.

cantrip-glow-name = Luminous Orb
cantrip-glow-description = Creates a short-lived luminous ball of light. Decays after 25 seconds.

cantrip-spark-name = Ember
cantrip-spark-description = Creates a short-lived flame suitable for use as an ignition source. Decays after 5 seconds.

cantrip-message-name = Psychic Whisper
cantrip-message-description = Transmits a secret message into the mind of a single target.